OL,3,CTrans charity rapped over policy on
OL,4,Cchest binders for children
OL,6,FBut the Leeds-based charity was
OL,7,Fcleared of misconduct, with the
OL,8,Fchairwoman of the organisation's
OL,9,Ftrustees saying they are "relieved"
OL,10,Fthe investigation is "finally over".
OL,12,FMermaids, established in 1995,
OL,13,Fdescribes itself as a charity
OL,14,Fsupporting trans, non-binary and
OL,15,Fgender-diverse children, young people
OL,16,Fand their families.
OL,18,FIt has an income of almost #2.3million
OL,19,Fand said it currently supports more
OL,20,Fthan 10,000 people every year.
