OL,3,CTrans charity rapped over policy on
OL,4,Cchest binders for children
OL,6,FAn inquiry was opened into the charity
OL,7,Fin 2022 after what the commission
OL,8,Fdescribed as "critical media articles"
OL,9,Fand complaints from the public raising
OL,10,Fconcerns around chest-binding services
OL,11,Fand the online support Mermaids was
OL,12,Foffering to young people.
OL,14,FThe Telegraph newspaper had reported
OL,15,Fthe charity had been offering binders
OL,16,Fto children as young as 13 despite
OL,17,Ftheir parents saying they opposed the
OL,18,Fpractice.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@fO]
