OL,3,CTrans charity rapped over policy on
OL,4,Cchest binders for children
OL,6,FConcerns were raised in Parliament,
OL,7,Fwith then-Conservative MP Miriam Cates
OL,8,Falleging "serious safeguarding
OL,9,Ffailures" and then-prime minister Liz
OL,10,FTruss saying the allegations "should
OL,11,Fbe properly looked at".
OL,13,FThe watchdog's report, published on
OL,14,FThursday, said the charity had issued
OL,15,F125 binders ` used to flatten breasts
OL,16,Fwith constrictive materials to make
OL,17,Fthe person more male-presenting `
OL,18,Fbetween January 2021 and September
OL,19,F2022.
