OL,7,Fto what the charity termed
OL,8,F"unsupported young persons", meaning
OL,9,Fthose under the age of 19 whose
OL,10,Fparents or carers were not supportive
OL,11,Fof the young person's gender identity
OL,12,For expression.
OL,14,FFifteen of those went to children aged
OL,15,Fbetween 13 and 16.
