OL,4,Cchest binders for children
OL,6,FWhile the charity argued this was done
OL,7,Fin an attempt to reduce harm to the
OL,8,Fyoung person, the commission said such
OL,9,Fa lack of transparency "can be
OL,10,Fproblematic and could potentially
OL,11,Fundermine the credibility of the
OL,12,Fcharity".
OL,14,FIt said the media attention following
OL,15,Fthis had "significantly damaged the
OL,16,Fcharity's reputation and could have
OL,17,Fbeen avoided".
