OL,6,FThe charity suspended the service in
OL,7,FSeptember 2022 "following adverse
OL,8,Fpublicity regarding the service and to
OL,9,Fprotect its staff who had been subject
OL,10,Fto threatening calls, emails and web
OL,11,Fchat contacts as a result of the
OL,12,Fadverse publicity", and formally ended
OL,13,Fit in October the following year.
