OL,3,CTrans charity rapped over policy on
OL,4,Cchest binders for children
OL,6,FThe watchdog said if the charity does
OL,7,Fever resume its supply of binders to
OL,8,Fyoung people in future, its policy
OL,9,Fshould reflect the findings of the
OL,10,FCass Review, which recommended that
OL,11,Fparents should be actively involved in
OL,12,Fsuch decisions around social
OL,13,Ftransitioning unless there are strong
OL,14,Fgrounds to believe that this could put
OL,15,Fthe young person at risk.
