OL,3,CTrans charity rapped over policy on
OL,4,Cchest binders for children
OL,6,FElsewhere in its 22-page report, the
OL,7,Fcommission said it had ordered
OL,8,FMermaids to review statements on its
OL,9,Fwebsite about puberty blockers being
OL,10,F"an internationally recognised safe,
OL,11,Freversible healthcare option".
OL,13,FThe watchdog said the charity had been
OL,14,F"unclear" about whether the
OL,15,Finformation it was providing was a
OL,16,Fstatement of fact or Mermaids' own
OL,17,Fopinion, and said that by law
OL,18,Fcharities are required to ensure
OL,19,Finformation provided on an educational
OL,20,Fbasis is accurate, evidence-based and
OL,21,Fbalanced.
