OL,4,Cchest binders for children
OL,6,FThe charity "should have mechanisms in
OL,7,Fplace to keep their position under
OL,8,Freview as this is clearly an area of
OL,9,Fmedicine where there is ongoing
OL,10,Fdevelopment and change", the watchdog
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FReferences to puberty blockers and
OL,14,Freversibility have been removed from
OL,15,Fthe charity's website.
OL,17,FThe commission said its findings of
OL,18,Fmismanagement related to trustee
OL,19,Ffailures to address internal issues
OL,20,Faround culture and inclusivity at the
OL,21,Fcharity.
