OL,3,CTrans charity rapped over policy on
OL,4,Cchest binders for children
OL,6,FIt also said there had been a failure
OL,7,Fto carry out sufficient due diligence
OL,8,Fchecks when recruiting trustees,
OL,9,Freferring to an incident where an ex-
OL,10,Ftrustee of the charity, known as Dr
OL,11,FBreslow, had spoken at a conference
OL,12,Forganised by a paedophile support
OL,13,Fgroup before being appointed.
OL,15,FThe charity, which said it only became
OL,16,Faware of his attendance at that event
OL,17,Fwhen a news story was published,
OL,18,Freleased a statement at the time, in
OL,19,F2022, saying he "should never have
OL,20,Fbeen appointed to the board".
